D:\{(x,y) ~|~ 0 \leq y \leq x, 0 \leq x \leq 1\}
 \begin{align} \iint_D (x + y)\ dx\ dy&=\int_{x=0}^1\int_{y=0}^x (x+y)\ dy\ dx\\ &=\int_{x=0}^1\left[xy+\frac{1}{2}y^2\right]_{y=0}^x \ dx\\ &=\int_{x=0}^1\left(\frac{3}{2}x^2\right)\ dx\\ &=\left[\frac{1}{2}x^3\right]_{x=0}^1\\ &=\boxed{\color{blue}{\Large\frac{1}{2}}} \end{align} 
